data.description: Nestled in the Northwest's natural beauty, this home in Clearwood's gated community is a serene retreat. This home is tucked away on a tranquil cul-de-sac with a short trail leading to one of 6 private beaches. A large primary suite, 5-piece bath, and walk-in closet showcase comfort and style. A well-designed layout includes an upstairs laundry room, a versatile loft, and a 2-car garage. All appliances are included for a seamless move-in. Outside, a low-maintenance yard with a fenced backyard, deck, fire pit, and storage shed awaits. Clearwood offers residents private amenities including a swimming pool, 3 lakes, a boat launch, trails, playgrounds, sports courts, and more. Sellers offer $10,000 concessions and an assumable loan at 3.75%.
